title: Animated Goblin Warrior
description: This character has 30 animations. Model with armor, 2 shields and 2 maces - 3,010 polygons, 5,402 triangles and 2,900 vertexes Textures: diffuse, specular, and normals maps. Textures are TIF file format 2048x2048 - body and 1024x1024 - for all armor parts together, 1024x1024for shield, 512X512 for mace. 12 textures at all. a href="http://www.youtube.com/user/MycroSlonik#p/a/u/0/QdsWluJGJtc ">See it on video!
